1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available.]

2
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:55,520
[Crossroad Bistro]

3
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:01,280
I won't ride a motorcycle anymore.

4
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:02,280
I'll drive this instead.

5
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:04,760
You won't have a cold nose ever again.

6
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,040
First a house, then a home.

7
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:06,960
Great.

8
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:08,479
We've got a house.

9
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:12,360
What medicine did you take?

10
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:14,400
You are so paranoid.

11
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,960
I wasn't hiding anything from you.

12
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:19,280
You writers are so impressive.

13
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,360
You don't have to work anymore.

14
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:22,280
I'll write and provide for you.

15
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,440
I'll pick a photo of yours

16
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:24,560
and print it in a larger format, okay?

17
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,920
Are you okay

18
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:28,800
with the nude scene?

19
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:29,920
If you don't do this film,

20
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:32,040
I'll cancel my flight for tomorrow.

21
00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:32,960
I thought

22
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:35,480
we are doing a back shot.

23
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:36,360
You are right.

24
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:38,200
Life is all about pursuing happiness.

25
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:40,720
I give up.

26
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:42,280
I miss you.

27
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:47,240
[Ep28]

28
00:02:48,440 --> 00:02:50,640
P2P scams happen every day.

29
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:52,000
But I didn't expect that

30
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,560
your family would be the victim.

31
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:56,320
It gives me such a headache.

32
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:59,920
The scammer is the son of my dad's colleague.

33
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,800
My dad thought he wouldn't be tricked

34
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:02,800
since he knows that guy so well.

35
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:03,880
Who'd ever thought?

36
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:06,280
My dad's been working hard for 30 years

37
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,560
and now he's lost all his savings.

38
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,680
My dad was the guarantor

39
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:12,040
for the loans of our relatives.

40
00:03:12,600 --> 00:03:13,360
Now, they are

41
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,840
nowhere to be found,

42
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:17,000
and my family has to take full responsibility.

43
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:21,360
How are you doing?

44
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:23,480
Well,

45
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:26,040
I've used all my savings from working abroad

46
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:26,960
to help him with the debt.

47
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:30,160
How much more do you need?

48
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:31,640
I can help you.

49
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:33,079
I didn't mean that.

50
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:35,840
I've paid most of the debt.

51
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:37,640
Money isn't what's at stake now,

52
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,920
but my mom's condition.

53
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:44,440
My mom was so worried that she got sick.

54
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,320
I think

55
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:46,880
I should stay here and take care of her.

56
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:47,920
But if I stay,

57
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:49,360
I need to find a job.

58
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:51,640
I've left China for so many years

59
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:53,480
and already lost touch with friends here.

60
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:55,480
Now I came back without notice.

61
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:57,560
I feel too embarrassed to ask them

62
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:02,680
for any job opportunities.

63
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,920
I saw Xiaoyu just now.

64
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:08,400
She seems happy.

65
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:10,240
And she just recovered.

66
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:12,840
I struggled for a while

67
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:15,040
but I just couldn't ask her.

68
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:16,240
I've been thinking,

69
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:18,079
and

70
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:21,440
you're the only one that might help me.

71
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:24,480
You can find a job easily.

72
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:27,000
But I can't afford to waste time.

73
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:29,920
Look who's here!

74
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,120
Gu.

75
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:33,520
Peihong,

76
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:35,159
what brings you back here?

77
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:38,680
Try the snacks.

78
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:39,360
Go on.

79
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,680
Are you here just to give me snacks?

80
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,880
No.

81
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:45,040
Someone brought me snacks.

82
00:04:45,320 --> 00:04:47,280
I heard that there's a girl in your office.

83
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:48,640
I thought Bao Xue is here.

84
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:49,960
Who'd have thought?

85
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,800
It's our talented Ms. Shen.

86
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:52,760
Ole Gu.

87
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,159
It's been years since we last met.

88
00:04:54,159 --> 00:04:55,360
But you're still cheeky

89
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:57,000
as ever.

90
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:58,040
Come on.

91
00:04:58,400 --> 00:04:59,360
I've changed.

92
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,560
I am getting old.

93
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:03,160
I blame you guys.

94
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:04,440
You call me

95
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:05,800
Ole Gu all the time.

96
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,160
But you just call him Yu.

97
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:08,960
Now, look what happened?

98
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:11,400
I am only three years older than him.

99
00:05:12,080 --> 00:05:13,120
But when we are together,

100
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,680
I look like his uncle, right?

101
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:17,760
All jokes aside,

102
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,280
how long

103
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,600
are you planning to stay?

104
00:05:20,840 --> 00:05:22,760
Peihong is back for good.

105
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,120
We were

106
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,520
talking about finding her a job.

107
00:05:26,440 --> 00:05:27,600
I think...

108
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,680
Hold your thought.

109
00:05:29,080 --> 00:05:30,520
Do as I say.

110
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:32,600
Our firm

111
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,680
could use a hand.

112
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:35,320
HR is recruiting as we speak.

113
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,720
I interviewed some candidates

114
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,920
but none of them are good.

115
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:41,680
If you don't mind working here,

116
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:43,200
then don't bother taking his nonsense advice.

117
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,920
You can just work here.

118
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,440
Why is my advice nonsense?

119
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:47,520
I was about to suggest the same.

120
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,560
Then we're all on the same page.

121
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:52,680
Is it appropriate

122
00:05:54,440 --> 00:05:55,520
that I work here?

123
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,320
What is

124
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:59,000
inappropriate about that?

125
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:00,800
If he says so,

126
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:02,120
then I don't have a problem with it at all.

127
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:03,800
It was ancient history

128
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:05,400
between you two.

129
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:07,560
Who says you can't advance your career in the same firm

130
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,160
as your ex?

131
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:10,400
Right?

132
00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:12,840
To be honest,

133
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:15,640
he's already run out of design ideas

134
00:06:15,640 --> 00:06:17,280
other than those he learned in Europe.

135
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:18,800
We are in need

136
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,560
of some new blood.

137
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,680
If it's okay with you,

138
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,840
we can skip the interview.

139
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,080
Just give us a number.

140
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:27,240
As long as it's reasonable,

141
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:29,040
I'll make it happen.

142
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:31,320
A number?

143
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:35,080
I am lousy at doing that.

144
00:06:35,080 --> 00:06:36,880
I'd feel embarrassed.

145
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,080
I think

146
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:39,480
you can make that decision.

147
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:40,760
Me?

148
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,400
What do you think?

149
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:50,040
Peihong is so talented

150
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:52,320
and we're asking her

151
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:53,600
to work as an employee.

152
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,920
That's beneath her, right?

153
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:57,560
What do you think, uncle?

154
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:01,480
I suggest

155
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:03,840
maybe we can

156
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:05,800
sell 5%

157
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:08,000
of each of our shares to her

158
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,680
at the original stock price.

159
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:13,720
This way, we'll be partners.

160
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:20,960
How about this, Gu?

161
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:24,400
Don't ask her to buy shares.

162
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:26,080
I will give 10%

163
00:07:26,080 --> 00:07:27,280
of my shares to her.

164
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,200
You're a real man!

165
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,240
Such a good friend!

166
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:33,120
I'm fine with that. What do you say, Peihong?

167
00:07:37,159 --> 00:07:38,600
Then, that's settled.

168
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:41,120
I'll ask the lawyers to draft a contract.

169
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,880
I gotta go now.

170
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:44,920
I've got a meeting.

171
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:45,720
Peihong.

172
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,240
I'll treat you to dinner

173
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:48,360
tomorrow.

174
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:50,960
I am meeting with Dai Xiaoyu tomorrow.

175
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:52,360
All the better.

176
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,080
Dinner together.

177
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:53,800
My treat!

178
00:07:55,159 --> 00:07:56,520
That's settled. See you.

179
00:07:58,360 --> 00:08:00,720
That cheapskate rarely pays for dinner.

180
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:01,680
Let him.

181
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:03,920
Thank you.

182
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:07,160
Grandma.

183
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,480
That's a lot of dumplings.

184
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,880
I want to make sure we have enough.

185
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:12,520
The last time

186
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:14,000
we invited two young men

187
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,600
to have dumplings

188
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:17,440
was 28 years ago.

189
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:19,360
Back then,

190
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,640
you were only two years old.

191
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:23,400
Bao Xue's parents hadn't got married

192
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:25,400
and were here for Lunar New Year for the first time.

193
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:27,320
Granny, does your memory serve you right?

194
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:28,920
We had dumplings together

195
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,800
to celebrate New Year after that.

196
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:31,320
But then,

197
00:08:31,840 --> 00:08:33,919
they were no young men anymore.

198
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,679
Now I get it.

199
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,080
By the way,

200
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:41,720
do you still remember

201
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:42,559
Shen Peihong,

202
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:43,440
my roommate in Norway?

203
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:45,560
She's in Beijing now.

204
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:46,760
I know.

205
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:48,040
Yu Songyang told me.

206
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:50,320
You're having dinner tomorrow, right?

207
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,040
Yeah.

208
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,240
You don't mind, do you?

209
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:57,160
It's just dinner with old schoolmates.

210
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:58,520
There will be other people, too.

211
00:08:58,520 --> 00:08:59,360
Besides,

212
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:00,640
I will be watching him.

213
00:09:00,640 --> 00:09:01,800
Why would I mind?

214
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:02,960
You'll be there?

215
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:04,440
Of course.

216
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:06,120
Yu Songyang invited me.

217
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,040
So, why not?

218
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:08,680
I'd seem petty if I didn't go.

219
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:09,960
Sis, you're so generous.

220
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,600
Of course.

221
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:13,240
Give me some chores.

222
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:14,440
I am boring.

223
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,040
You?

224
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:15,960
Come on.

225
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:18,040
We'll be grateful if you don't make a mess.

226
00:09:19,800 --> 00:09:20,480
Leave.

227
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,840
Go stay with your boyfriend.

228
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:22,880
Have a chat or something.

229
00:09:24,280 --> 00:09:25,880
I don't know what to say to him.

230
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:28,120
I came here because I felt awkward over there.

231
00:09:28,800 --> 00:09:31,160
When you're in love, you don't need to talk.

232
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:34,000
You can just stare at each other and feel happy.

233
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,440
That'd be so awkward.

234
00:09:35,760 --> 00:09:37,320
What are you mumbling about?

235
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:39,440
You want chores, right?

236
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,440
Set the table.

237
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:42,640
Okay.

238
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,080
She rarely does that.

239
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:51,600
The Wurenbacher tastes good.

240
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,440
Want one?

241
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:53,440
I need to drive.

242
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:54,360
You go ahead.

243
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:56,640
You're right not to drink if you're driving later.

244
00:09:57,880 --> 00:09:58,600
Bao Xue told me

245
00:09:58,600 --> 00:09:59,800
you're going on a business trip tomorrow.

246
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:01,560
Yeah.

247
00:10:01,560 --> 00:10:02,800
I was supposed to go in October,

248
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:03,880
but

249
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,520
it got postponed.

250
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:06,840
How long are you going?

251
00:10:07,520 --> 00:10:08,520
I won't be back till March.

252
00:10:08,520 --> 00:10:09,840
It takes longer to film a costume drama.

253
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,920
Why is that?

254
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:14,480
It's different from modern drama.

255
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:17,280
Taste this.

256
00:10:17,800 --> 00:10:18,360
Without chopsticks?

257
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:19,040
I forgot.

258
00:10:19,040 --> 00:10:19,800
Just grab one.

259
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:23,720
It's hot.

260
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,080
So?

261
00:10:30,400 --> 00:10:31,240
Yum.

262
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:32,040
Amazing.

263
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:34,240
Granny, it tastes perfect.

264
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:36,800
Am I a lab rat to you?

265
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:41,160
Dad makes the best dinner.

266
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:45,000
The Fish of Fortune is done.

267
00:10:47,560 --> 00:10:49,200
Dad, can I try it?

268
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:50,560
You're getting better at cooking.

269
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,720
Are you hungry?

270
00:10:53,400 --> 00:10:54,240
The dumplings are ready.

271
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,000
I'll go get them.

272
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:58,080
Try the fish dad made.

273
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:00,720
It's hot.

274
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:03,240
All done.

275
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:04,640
Dig in.

276
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:06,240
I was very efficient, right?

277
00:11:10,880 --> 00:11:12,520
How did it go this afternoon

278
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:13,520
at the company?

279
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:15,360
Ma doesn't think I'm writing fast enough.

280
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:17,960
He suggested I write somewhere alone.

281
00:11:18,560 --> 00:11:19,400
Alone?

282
00:11:19,640 --> 00:11:20,640
Where?

283
00:11:20,640 --> 00:11:21,600
Aranya.

284
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:23,800
Aranya?

285
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:26,280
You're going to the seaside in winter?

286
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,840
That's when it's quiet there.

287
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:28,880
How can I write

288
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:30,280
with so many visitors in summer?

289
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,120
You said yes?

290
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:33,280
Not yet.

291
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:34,960
I had thought

292
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:36,240
I'd finish the two-month work

293
00:11:36,400 --> 00:11:37,920
in a month.

294
00:11:38,400 --> 00:11:40,120
But it didn't go as planned.

295
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:42,000
Back then, no one rushed me to write.

296
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:43,800
I used to write some every day.

297
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:46,000
But now,

298
00:11:46,560 --> 00:11:47,840
I often stay up all night in front of the laptop

299
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:49,360
without writing anything.

300
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:51,440
Yeah.

301
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:53,360
There are too many distractions at home.

302
00:11:53,880 --> 00:11:55,480
That's why I can't leave.

303
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:57,160
If I leave you in charge,

304
00:11:58,520 --> 00:11:59,560
you'll go crazy.

305
00:12:00,640 --> 00:12:01,680
Making money is...

306
00:12:01,680 --> 00:12:02,800
It's a shitty business.

307
00:12:03,920 --> 00:12:04,880
We're eating!

308
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:06,000
Language!

309
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,440
Where did you learn that word?

310
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:10,800
I didn't teach him to say that.

311
00:12:20,120 --> 00:12:20,880
Alright.

312
00:12:20,880 --> 00:12:22,040
I'm fine. You can go back.

313
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:23,640
What are you doing?

314
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:25,600
You'll leave tomorrow.

315
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:26,680
I'll help you pack.

316
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:29,320
Let's go.

317
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:50,320
Have a rest.

318
00:12:50,320 --> 00:12:51,800
I'll do it myself.

319
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:52,960
Allow me.

320
00:12:54,520 --> 00:12:56,560
Do you think I am too slow?

321
00:12:56,920 --> 00:12:58,400
Absolutely not.

322
00:12:58,960 --> 00:13:00,440
I just thought you could use a rest

323
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:02,720
since you just recovered.

324
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:04,840
I'm fine.

325
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:05,600
I'll do it.

326
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:07,880
It won't take long.

327
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:09,760
Go take a rest.

328
00:13:11,400 --> 00:13:12,880
Go.

329
00:13:26,280 --> 00:13:27,760
It's late.

330
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:30,040
I'll pack the rest.

331
00:13:30,040 --> 00:13:31,320
Let me drive you back.

332
00:13:32,800 --> 00:13:34,720
Do you have a new toothbrush here?

333
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:36,560
I...

334
00:13:36,560 --> 00:13:38,040
I am not going back tonight.

335
00:13:45,160 --> 00:13:46,360
Xiaoyu.

336
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:48,120
Come.

337
00:13:49,040 --> 00:13:49,880
Sit over here.

338
00:14:00,640 --> 00:14:02,560
I've been doing a lot of thinking.

339
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:05,120
I have.

340
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:09,440
I don't want to say this,

341
00:14:11,800 --> 00:14:13,280
but I have to.

342
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:16,040
It's for our own good.

343
00:14:18,200 --> 00:14:19,600
What is it?

344
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:23,120
I think we should break up.

345
00:14:27,320 --> 00:14:28,720
Why?

346
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:30,120
Hear me out.

347
00:14:30,880 --> 00:14:32,280
Recently,

348
00:14:32,680 --> 00:14:34,080
I've been observing you.

349
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:36,520
I can feel

350
00:14:36,520 --> 00:14:39,320
that you're trying so hard to fall in love with me

351
00:14:39,560 --> 00:14:41,160
and be my girlfriend.

352
00:14:41,680 --> 00:14:43,880
But you won't develop feelings for me
 through pretending.

353
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:45,640
You either love me

354
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:47,240
or you don't.

355
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:48,640
I can see it.

356
00:14:53,520 --> 00:14:55,160
I admit that I love you.

357
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:57,280
And I don't want to lose you.

358
00:14:57,280 --> 00:14:58,840
But if we keep doing this,

359
00:14:58,840 --> 00:15:00,240
you'll be miserable.

360
00:15:01,520 --> 00:15:03,400
We won't be happy.

361
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:10,240
Remember you asked me to change the photo?

362
00:15:11,440 --> 00:15:13,160
You were trying to tell me

363
00:15:13,160 --> 00:15:14,560
you were jealous, right?

364
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:16,840
You were afraid that I might think

365
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:18,120
you don't care for me.

366
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:20,280
But

367
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:23,240
you started to play with your phone

368
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:25,320
before I even put the old photo away.

369
00:15:25,840 --> 00:15:28,080
That means you were only pretending to be jealous.

370
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:31,440
You help me with all the packing.

371
00:15:31,920 --> 00:15:33,760
I know you're trying to prove to me

372
00:15:33,760 --> 00:15:36,080
that you care for me.

373
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:37,440
But

374
00:15:37,440 --> 00:15:38,840
these are just methods.

375
00:15:39,320 --> 00:15:41,080
They are not from your heart.

376
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:45,360
During dinner tonight,

377
00:15:47,840 --> 00:15:49,640
we talked about Bao Xue

378
00:15:49,640 --> 00:15:51,600
and Yu Songyang getting married.

379
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:54,520
Did you notice the way they looked at each other?

380
00:15:54,800 --> 00:15:56,200
That was the look of two people

381
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:57,440
who are truly in love.

382
00:15:59,520 --> 00:16:01,640
But I glanced at you,

383
00:16:02,440 --> 00:16:04,360
and you were avoiding eye contact with me.

384
00:16:05,680 --> 00:16:07,080
You weren't pretending at that moment.

385
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:09,320
You did that without even knowing it.

386
00:16:11,760 --> 00:16:13,600
And that's because you don't love me.

387
00:16:14,400 --> 00:16:15,800
Right?

388
00:16:18,040 --> 00:16:20,240
I can pretend I haven't noticed any of these,

389
00:16:21,360 --> 00:16:23,400
and we can keep on living like this.

390
00:16:23,920 --> 00:16:25,520
But I think if I do that,

391
00:16:26,520 --> 00:16:28,280
I'd be too selfish.

392
00:16:29,520 --> 00:16:30,720
Xiaoyu,

393
00:16:31,880 --> 00:16:33,080
everything I've done for you,

394
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:35,120
I did them willingly.

395
00:16:35,840 --> 00:16:38,280
I don't expect anything in return.

396
00:16:40,480 --> 00:16:42,200
If we stay together,

397
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:44,000
I hope it's because

398
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,680
you truly love me

399
00:16:45,680 --> 00:16:47,520
rather than feeling guilty.

400
00:16:48,720 --> 00:16:50,640
I don't want you to be with me so that you can repay me.

401
00:16:53,760 --> 00:16:55,160
Do you understand?

402
00:17:04,520 --> 00:17:06,640
I am sorry, Liu.

403
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:10,280
I think I owe you too much.

404
00:17:19,520 --> 00:17:21,160
When I finish shooting,

405
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:22,800
buy me a drink.

406
00:17:29,360 --> 00:17:31,280
I'll buy you as much drink as you'd like.

407
00:17:52,920 --> 00:17:53,800
Xiaoyu,

408
00:17:55,840 --> 00:17:57,200
I love you.

409
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:02,200
This will be the last time I say it to you.

410
00:18:06,320 --> 00:18:07,720
I won't say it anymore.

411
00:18:42,600 --> 00:18:44,280
Go to bed.

412
00:18:46,080 --> 00:18:46,960
I fell asleep.

413
00:18:47,880 --> 00:18:48,880
Even coffee doesn't work now.

414
00:18:51,760 --> 00:18:52,760
I am immune to caffeine now.

415
00:18:54,240 --> 00:18:55,800
I'll finish this paragraph first.

416
00:18:59,240 --> 00:19:00,320
Go to Aranya.

417
00:19:01,480 --> 00:19:02,120
No.

418
00:19:02,120 --> 00:19:03,640
Our family needs me.

419
00:19:06,680 --> 00:19:07,880
Do as I say.

420
00:19:09,760 --> 00:19:10,720
Just go.

421
00:19:11,400 --> 00:19:12,920
Or you won't be able to finish your book,

422
00:19:13,200 --> 00:19:14,560
and you won't be able to take care of us.

423
00:19:14,880 --> 00:19:16,240
Plus, you might get sick.

424
00:19:16,240 --> 00:19:16,960
It's a lose-lose for all.

425
00:19:21,080 --> 00:19:22,160
If you go, at least

426
00:19:22,160 --> 00:19:23,720
you can focus on one thing

427
00:19:23,920 --> 00:19:25,000
and be more efficient.

428
00:19:26,120 --> 00:19:27,400
You can come back when you finish it.

429
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:28,880
I'll take care of the kids.

430
00:19:31,760 --> 00:19:33,840
Then, you can visit me on weekends.

431
00:19:35,080 --> 00:19:36,200
We'll go find you

432
00:19:36,200 --> 00:19:37,240
when you're almost done.

433
00:19:39,560 --> 00:19:40,840
Let's go to bed.

434
00:19:41,040 --> 00:19:41,720
Yeah.

435
00:19:42,960 --> 00:19:43,840
I'll save the file.

436
00:19:49,840 --> 00:19:50,920
You must be exhausted.

437
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:51,920
You did great.

438
00:20:02,080 --> 00:20:05,080
Dai Xiaoyu, you're so slow!

439
00:20:06,240 --> 00:20:08,040
Are you ready or not?

440
00:20:09,800 --> 00:20:10,760
I know.

441
00:20:12,040 --> 00:20:13,480
Thank you for understanding.

442
00:20:13,480 --> 00:20:15,640
You said five minutes.

443
00:20:15,640 --> 00:20:17,440
How many five minutes has it been?

444
00:20:18,160 --> 00:20:18,760
Okay.

445
00:20:19,120 --> 00:20:20,400
I'll visit you before Lunar New Year.

446
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:22,760
Great, bye.

447
00:20:26,440 --> 00:20:27,760
Stop rushing me.

448
00:20:27,840 --> 00:20:29,400
I was on the phone with Hua.

449
00:20:29,560 --> 00:20:30,200
Hua?

450
00:20:32,120 --> 00:20:33,200
She wasn't

451
00:20:33,200 --> 00:20:34,960
angry with me about last time, was she?

452
00:20:35,280 --> 00:20:35,960
She wasn't.

453
00:20:36,440 --> 00:20:37,320
She's very understanding.

454
00:20:41,440 --> 00:20:41,960
So?

455
00:20:41,960 --> 00:20:43,600
When are you going to work for her?

456
00:20:44,320 --> 00:20:46,520
I told her that Mr. Chai has been good to me.

457
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:48,360
I'd be ungrateful if I leave now.

458
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:50,200
I'll stay and help him for a while longer.

459
00:20:51,320 --> 00:20:53,360
Hua said that since it's the end of the year,

460
00:20:53,760 --> 00:20:55,960
I can wait after the New Year vacation
 to make a decision.

461
00:20:58,040 --> 00:21:00,000
So, Hua likes you a lot.

462
00:21:00,480 --> 00:21:01,280
The Hua I know

463
00:21:01,280 --> 00:21:02,240
is someone

464
00:21:02,240 --> 00:21:03,080
who wouldn't wait

465
00:21:03,080 --> 00:21:05,200
more than one day to do the things she wants.

466
00:21:07,160 --> 00:21:08,000
Let's go.

467
00:21:08,600 --> 00:21:09,640
Where are we going?

468
00:21:09,640 --> 00:21:10,600
Afternoon tea?

469
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:12,840
Let's go shopping.

470
00:21:13,120 --> 00:21:14,120
Shopping?

471
00:21:14,120 --> 00:21:16,080
Can't you just buy things online?

472
00:21:16,920 --> 00:21:18,880
Shanshan's birthday is next month.

473
00:21:18,880 --> 00:21:20,440
Let's pick a gift for her.

474
00:21:20,600 --> 00:21:21,920
Great.

475
00:21:22,600 --> 00:21:24,200
Have you thought about what to buy her?

476
00:21:24,480 --> 00:21:25,160
No.

477
00:21:25,360 --> 00:21:26,160
No?

478
00:21:26,880 --> 00:21:28,160
She likes watches.

479
00:21:28,960 --> 00:21:29,880
Too expensive.

480
00:21:30,920 --> 00:21:31,960
I'm here.

481
00:21:32,080 --> 00:21:33,000
I'm in the house.

482
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:33,680
You're here?

483
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:34,720
How's everything?

484
00:21:34,920 --> 00:21:35,840
I'll show you.

485
00:21:39,080 --> 00:21:40,920
Here's the couch, the TV,

486
00:21:45,760 --> 00:21:46,720
and the sea.

487
00:21:47,600 --> 00:21:48,480
Nice.

488
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:49,400
Is this where you live?

489
00:21:50,280 --> 00:21:51,080
What are you doing?

490
00:21:51,440 --> 00:21:52,600
I just finished a meeting.

491
00:21:53,640 --> 00:21:54,240
Alright.

492
00:21:54,240 --> 00:21:56,080
I'll unpack and then start to write.

493
00:21:56,240 --> 00:21:57,560
Don't be late to pick up the kids.

494
00:21:57,800 --> 00:21:58,680
I won't. Don't worry.

495
00:21:58,880 --> 00:21:59,600
I won't be late.

496
00:22:00,920 --> 00:22:02,200
Bye.

497
00:22:19,360 --> 00:22:20,520
I just realized that

498
00:22:20,960 --> 00:22:22,760
this is the first time I've lived in a hotel alone

499
00:22:22,760 --> 00:22:24,720
since we got married.

500
00:22:26,600 --> 00:22:29,640
[Crossroad Bistro]

501
00:22:29,800 --> 00:22:30,720
Try this.

502
00:22:30,720 --> 00:22:31,960
This is our specialty.

503
00:22:31,960 --> 00:22:32,720
Okay.

504
00:22:34,240 --> 00:22:34,840
Come on.

505
00:22:35,080 --> 00:22:36,320
Let's fill our glasses.

506
00:22:36,520 --> 00:22:37,360
I'll propose a toast.

507
00:22:39,640 --> 00:22:40,440
First,

508
00:22:40,760 --> 00:22:42,040
I want to toast Shen Peihong,

509
00:22:42,560 --> 00:22:44,120
our goddess

510
00:22:44,920 --> 00:22:46,120
who's traveled thousands of miles

511
00:22:46,320 --> 00:22:47,800
and came back to her homeland with glory.

512
00:22:49,800 --> 00:22:51,720
Such weird word choices.

513
00:22:51,720 --> 00:22:52,400
I was being poetic.

514
00:22:52,680 --> 00:22:53,280
Thank you.

515
00:22:53,280 --> 00:22:54,080
Welcome back.

516
00:22:54,240 --> 00:22:55,360
You've started drinking already.

517
00:22:56,720 --> 00:22:57,680
This is Feng Xi,

518
00:22:57,680 --> 00:22:58,840
our partner.

519
00:22:59,280 --> 00:23:00,000
Hello.

520
00:23:00,880 --> 00:23:02,560
Feng Xi, have dinner with us.

521
00:23:02,760 --> 00:23:03,720
I'm good.

522
00:23:03,720 --> 00:23:05,080
There are many customers out there.

523
00:23:05,080 --> 00:23:06,360
Enjoy yourselves.

524
00:23:07,880 --> 00:23:09,720
Come join us when you're less busy.

525
00:23:09,720 --> 00:23:10,440
Okay.

526
00:23:13,480 --> 00:23:15,320
Why is every partner of yours

527
00:23:15,360 --> 00:23:16,760
a beautiful lady?

528
00:23:17,360 --> 00:23:18,840
Don't get any ideas.

529
00:23:19,000 --> 00:23:20,320
She's taken.

530
00:23:20,320 --> 00:23:21,480
Come on.

531
00:23:22,560 --> 00:23:23,960
I was just giving praise.

532
00:23:24,240 --> 00:23:25,280
What are you talking about?

533
00:23:25,280 --> 00:23:27,000
Give me a break. I know you too well.

534
00:23:28,120 --> 00:23:29,400
The second toast

535
00:23:29,640 --> 00:23:32,040
is to Ms. Dai Xiaoyu.

536
00:23:32,800 --> 00:23:33,440
Me?

537
00:23:33,440 --> 00:23:35,920
We three were schoolmates
 at the architecture college.

538
00:23:36,560 --> 00:23:38,360
You were Peihong's roommate.

539
00:23:38,920 --> 00:23:39,840
I've heard

540
00:23:39,840 --> 00:23:41,400
so much about you.

541
00:23:41,560 --> 00:23:43,320
Now that I've finally met you, I'd be honored

542
00:23:46,120 --> 00:23:47,000
to add you on WeChat.

543
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:48,240
Come on. Cheers.

544
00:23:48,240 --> 00:23:48,800
Cheers.

545
00:23:48,800 --> 00:23:49,440
Cheers.

546
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:52,600
What's wrong with you today?

547
00:23:52,600 --> 00:23:53,960
You're so talkative today.

548
00:23:54,760 --> 00:23:55,600
What?

549
00:23:55,960 --> 00:23:57,960
Our company is joined with such a talented person.

550
00:23:58,000 --> 00:23:59,480
I am in a good mood!

551
00:24:00,280 --> 00:24:01,120
Give me a break.

552
00:24:01,440 --> 00:24:02,200
Fill your glass.

553
00:24:02,200 --> 00:24:03,520
Let's have a drink.

554
00:24:04,320 --> 00:24:05,560
Okay, allow me to fill your glass.

555
00:24:06,080 --> 00:24:06,720
Pace yourself.

556
00:24:06,720 --> 00:24:07,520
Yu,

557
00:24:08,120 --> 00:24:09,440
all jokes aside,

558
00:24:09,920 --> 00:24:12,760
you helped me convince Peihong to work with us,

559
00:24:12,760 --> 00:24:14,040
and you gave 10%

560
00:24:14,040 --> 00:24:16,360
of your shares to her.

561
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:18,800
Seriously, you're such a good friend.

562
00:24:21,680 --> 00:24:23,120
Sincerely, I raise my glass to you.

563
00:24:23,840 --> 00:24:25,080
We are a team in the future.

564
00:24:25,440 --> 00:24:26,480
Save the formalities.

565
00:24:26,560 --> 00:24:27,320
Peihong,

566
00:24:27,320 --> 00:24:29,520
shouldn't you drink to him as well?

567
00:24:30,560 --> 00:24:31,480
Of course.

568
00:24:32,840 --> 00:24:34,040
Cheers.

569
00:24:41,120 --> 00:24:42,040
Help yourselves.

570
00:24:42,840 --> 00:24:43,560
Gu.

571
00:24:43,880 --> 00:24:45,840
Drink less. Eat more.

572
00:24:46,080 --> 00:24:47,560
I'm fine. I am just too happy.

573
00:24:48,080 --> 00:24:48,800
Bao Xue.

574
00:24:49,640 --> 00:24:51,000
This one is to you.

575
00:24:52,200 --> 00:24:53,080
For what?

576
00:24:53,800 --> 00:24:55,400
For having a good eye.

577
00:24:55,760 --> 00:24:57,320
Yu Songyang

578
00:24:57,320 --> 00:24:58,480
is the perfect choice for a husband.

579
00:24:59,040 --> 00:24:59,800
He's loyal and generous

580
00:25:00,880 --> 00:25:01,960
to friends.

581
00:25:01,960 --> 00:25:03,200
He's reliable at work.

582
00:25:03,200 --> 00:25:03,960
And he

583
00:25:05,160 --> 00:25:05,840
loves you truly.

584
00:25:06,240 --> 00:25:06,760
Come on.

585
00:25:06,760 --> 00:25:07,760
