00:37:34,320 --> 00:37:36,440
Now she can't be nice to you?

876
00:37:40,320 --> 00:37:41,000
I think

877
00:37:41,040 --> 00:37:42,480
she just came to her senses

878
00:37:42,840 --> 00:37:44,280
and chose to believe you.

879
00:37:44,800 --> 00:37:46,240
Come to think of it,

880
00:37:46,240 --> 00:37:48,160
Bao Xue is young but considerate.

881
00:37:49,560 --> 00:37:51,080
If it were my wife,

882
00:37:51,080 --> 00:37:53,080
she'd make a scene.

883
00:37:53,200 --> 00:37:54,520
Do you even have a wife?

884
00:37:54,880 --> 00:37:55,800
My ex-wife.

885
00:37:55,880 --> 00:37:56,680
Alright?

886
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:59,680
Stop discriminating against divorced people.

887
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:01,600
My office is stinky because of your cigarette smell.

888
00:38:02,440 --> 00:38:03,800
Look at yourself.

889
00:38:06,160 --> 00:38:06,720
Peihong.

890
00:38:06,720 --> 00:38:07,560
You're here early.

891
00:38:07,840 --> 00:38:09,600
I came as soon as I dropped my mom home.

892
00:38:09,600 --> 00:38:10,240
Great.

893
00:38:10,240 --> 00:38:11,520
Have a seat.

894
00:38:12,480 --> 00:38:13,560
You come over here.

895
00:38:22,840 --> 00:38:24,600
Here are two contracts.

896
00:38:26,240 --> 00:38:28,200
One is the partnership contract.

897
00:38:28,560 --> 00:38:29,640
It's for you.

898
00:38:30,040 --> 00:38:31,640
The other is for the transfer of shares

899
00:38:32,040 --> 00:38:32,800
from Yu Songyang.

900
00:38:33,240 --> 00:38:33,800
Take it.

901
00:38:35,040 --> 00:38:36,200
You two

902
00:38:36,200 --> 00:38:37,000
shall read

903
00:38:37,000 --> 00:38:38,760
every word of it thoroughly.

904
00:38:39,160 --> 00:38:40,360
If everything in there is correct,

905
00:38:40,360 --> 00:38:41,240
you can sign the contract.

906
00:38:48,640 --> 00:38:50,040
I want to tell you something.

907
00:38:51,200 --> 00:38:53,360
I told you I'm gonna stay in China.

908
00:38:54,680 --> 00:38:56,160
I made the decision 'cause my mom was sick,

909
00:38:56,160 --> 00:38:57,040
and I was worried.

910
00:38:57,800 --> 00:38:59,400
Now that she's discharged

911
00:38:59,400 --> 00:39:01,000
and looks fine,

912
00:39:01,520 --> 00:39:02,600
I've decided

913
00:39:02,920 --> 00:39:03,680
to go back to Norway.

914
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:06,560
Peihong,

915
00:39:06,560 --> 00:39:07,760
please don't feel pressured.

916
00:39:07,760 --> 00:39:09,040
I've talked to Bao Xue.

917
00:39:09,040 --> 00:39:09,920
She won't...

918
00:39:10,360 --> 00:39:11,200
That's not it.

919
00:39:12,400 --> 00:39:14,840
It's just that I've been doing a lot of thinking.

920
00:39:15,360 --> 00:39:17,640
I've been abroad for so many years

921
00:39:17,960 --> 00:39:19,720
and I've got a stable job.

922
00:39:19,720 --> 00:39:20,880
I'm used to life back there.

923
00:39:20,960 --> 00:39:22,600
I'm afraid I won't adjust well

924
00:39:22,600 --> 00:39:24,120
if I come back to China.

925
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:24,960
So,

926
00:39:24,960 --> 00:39:26,080
it's not for any other reasons.

927
00:39:27,320 --> 00:39:29,360
I am here to say goodbye.

928
00:39:29,840 --> 00:39:30,680
For what it's worth,

929
00:39:30,680 --> 00:39:32,360
I'm deeply moved that

930
00:39:33,320 --> 00:39:34,480
you two are willing to help me.

931
00:39:35,800 --> 00:39:36,760
Peihong, is it...

932
00:39:36,760 --> 00:39:37,600
Stop it.

933
00:39:38,280 --> 00:39:39,400
You know me well, don't you?

934
00:39:39,800 --> 00:39:40,680
I've made up my mind.

935
00:39:40,680 --> 00:39:41,640
I've booked my flight.

936
00:39:45,920 --> 00:39:46,680
Okay.

937
00:39:47,360 --> 00:39:48,200
Peihong,

938
00:39:49,360 --> 00:39:50,760
I respect your decision.

939
00:39:52,520 --> 00:39:53,320
When are you leaving?

940
00:39:53,640 --> 00:39:54,480
We'll see you off.

941
00:39:55,080 --> 00:39:55,840
It's alright.

942
00:39:56,360 --> 00:39:57,560
You are busy.

943
00:39:57,560 --> 00:39:58,720
My parents will see me off.

944
00:40:02,120 --> 00:40:02,840
Please give this

945
00:40:02,840 --> 00:40:03,640
to Bao Xue.

946
00:40:08,560 --> 00:40:10,280
This is for Bao Xue.

947
00:40:13,280 --> 00:40:13,960
Okay.

948
00:40:14,720 --> 00:40:15,600
Guys,

949
00:40:16,160 --> 00:40:16,880
see you.

950
00:40:24,120 --> 00:40:24,800
Thanks.

951
00:40:25,200 --> 00:40:26,600
Take care of yourself.

952
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:43,040
Bye-bye.

953
00:40:43,920 --> 00:40:44,680
Take care.
